A comprehensive property and utilities management system built with Laravel for property managers, landlords, and building owners.

## 🚀 Features

### Core Management
- 🏢 Building and floor plan management
- 🏠 Unit/room tracking with status monitoring
- 👥 Tenant information and lease management
- 📄 Digital lease agreements and document storage

### Billing & Payments
- 💰 Automated bill generation and distribution
- 💳 Multiple payment method support (credit card, bank transfer, cash)
- 📅 Payment tracking and late fee calculation
- 🧾 Receipt generation and payment history

### Utilities Tracking
- ⚡ Electricity consumption monitoring
- 💧 Water usage tracking with leak detection
- 🔥 Gas consumption and safety monitoring
- 📊 Consumption analysis and reporting

### Maintenance
- 🔧 Maintenance request management
- 🛠️ Preventive maintenance scheduling
- 👷 Vendor management and rating system
- ⏱️ SLA tracking for maintenance requests

### Reports & Analytics
- 📈 Financial reports and revenue analysis
- 📊 Occupancy and vacancy reports
- 🔔 Smart alerts and notifications
- 📋 Custom report generation

## 🛠️ Technology Stack

- **Backend:** Laravel 10.x
- **Frontend:** Blade Templates, Vanilla JavaScript
- **Database:** MySQL
- **Authentication:** Laravel Session-based Auth
- **Styling:** Custom CSS with responsive design

## 📋 Prerequisites

- PHP 8.1 or higher
- Composer 2.x
- MySQL 5.7 or higher
- Node.js 16+ (for frontend assets)

